Myprotein Move Club Verified Club

Multisport   United Kingdom

Welcome to the Myprotein Move Club

This isn't just a run club. The Move Club is a community, a celebration of pushing boundaries, surpassing limits, and embracing a healthier lifestyle together.

What to Expect:

- 5km community run with special guests

- 6min Km Pace

- Free Myprotein products

Requirements:

The safety of our community is priority. We urge everyone to show consideration and support for their fellow attendees, and do ask everyone to sign a waiver to participate.
